descriptionNullable:
This is a zip file that contains 262 csv files.

It contains all the subtitles of Gintama (anime).
Translator teams: HorribleSubs and Yousei-raws.

Episodes: From 0 to 265 (included)

There are four columns: Number, Start time in milliseconds, End time in milliseconds, and Text.
